query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(cd cs p) NoMergeJoin(cd cs i p dd) */ select i.i_item_id,
avg(cs.cs_quantity) AS agg1,
avg(cs.cs_list_price) AS agg2,
avg(cs.cs_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
avg(cs.cs_sales_price) AS agg4
from customer_demographics AS cd
inner join catalog_sales AS cs
on cs.cs_bill_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk AND cd.cd_gender = 'M' AND cd.cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd.cd_education_status = 'College'
inner join promotion AS p
on cs.cs_promo_sk = p.p_promo_sk AND ( p.p_channel_email = 'N' OR p.p_channel_event = 'N')
inner join item AS i
on cs.cs_item_sk = i.i_item_sk
inner join date_dim AS dd
on cs.cs_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_year = 2001 group by i.i_item_id order by i.i_item_id LIMIT 100;
